    "This enhances the credibility and accuracy of the peer review process, ensuring that each resource is evaluated with a balance of diverse perspectives and expert judgment.",
    "Through these mechanisms, RiPPLE not only maintains the integrity of the peer assessment process but also actively involves students in critical evaluation, fostering a deeper engagement and understanding.",
    "Individual reviews within RiPPLE are structured around a comprehensive rubric (see Fig. 3), tailored to assess various dimensions of resource quality.",
    "The rubric incorporates multiple criteria, each specifically aligned with the nature of the resource being reviewed.",
    "For example, in the case of multiple-choice questions, one criterion assesses the quality and relevance of the options provided, while in worked examples the rubric examines the clarity and comprehensiveness of the intermediate steps."
